<div class="scp-image-block block-right" style="width:300px;"><a href="https://scp-wiki-cn.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-cn-1005/SCP-CN-1005"><img src="https://scp-wiki-cn.wdfiles.com/local--resized-images/scp-cn-1005/SCP-CN-1005/medium.jpg" style="width:300px;" alt="SCP-CN-1005" class="image" /></a>
